{% doc %}
  @prompt
    I'd like you to create a best-in-class design contest voting page. I want you to make it easy for me to upload images of designs that people have, and then I also want people to be able to vote on which design they like the best. When you click the button to vote, it prompts that you have to enter your email. Then we capture that within the Shopify system and also be great if we could have that connected to Klaviyo so have a third-party integration within here. Let's see what you can do. , when you click vote, the modal should pop up and it doesn't seem to be pls fix, better, but there is liquid error when modal pops up please fix, optimize for mobile with 2 product cards per row on mobile. Also give me ability to adjust the padding within the modal pop-up. Also give me the option to customize the thank you page after people submit their vote
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
